               <p>Look at the prisoner at the bar, do you recollect him? - I do.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178309100017"></xptr>Do you recollect his being here in February sessions last? - He was convicted in February sessions last.</p>
               <p>You are sure it is the same person? - Yes.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17830910-7-person144">
                  THOMAS
                   HARVEY
